Story: Visiting the Casts New page

  As a person of merbasts 
  I want to get to the new form
  So that I can upload new casts
  
  Scenario: Anonymous person visits the Casts New action
    Given an anonymous person
    
    When the person visits /casts/new
    
    Then the person should be redirected to: /login
  
  Scenario: An active person visits the Casts New action
    Given no people in the database
    And an active person

    When the person visits /casts/new

    Then the person should see the page: Casts new
    And the person should be logged in
    And the page should match the selector once: form[@action="/casts/"][@enctype="multipart/form-data"][@method="post"]
    And the page should have an input named: cast[title]
  
  Scenario: An active publisher visits the Casts New action
    Given an active publisher named: joe
    
    When the person visits /casts/new
    
    Then the person should see the page: Casts new